ion with 100 acres after mother's death. James bequeathed Henry's land if he didn't return from England-he did! Negro Dick to wife Katherine.   Son in law William George hath received 1560 lbs tobacco in part of estate of his grandfather in law Edwd Dale, I having noe Rect for it and if he will not be accountable for it, then he shall have no part of my estate only 1 shilling in full part of his wi\"},{\"t\":\"OTHER_EVENT\",\"ti\":\"Will Proved\",\"d\":\"14 November 1700\",\"pl\":\"Lancaster, Virginia, British Colonial America\",\"desc\":\"by the three witnesses\"},{\"t\":\"MILITARY_SERVICE\",\"ti\":\"\",\"d\":\"\",\"pl\":\"\",\"desc\":\"Virginia Militia - Captain\"},{\"t\":\"OCCUPATION\",\"ti\":\"\",\"d\":\"\",\"pl\":\"\",\"desc\":\"Tobacco Planter\"},{\"t\":\"OTHER_EVENT\",\"ti\":\"Edward Dale \",\"d\":\"\",\"pl\":\"\",\"desc\":\"\"},{\"t\":\"OTHER_EVENT\",\"ti\":\"Edward Dale gifts slave boys to Katherine and Thomas\",\"d\":\"\",\"pl\":\"\",\"desc\":\"\"},{\"t\":\"RESIDENCE\",\"ti\":\"\",\"d\":\"\",\"pl\":\"Lancaster, Virginia, British Colonial America\",\"desc\":\"Lancaster County, Virginia, British Colonial America\"},{\"t\":\"RESIDENCE\",\"ti\":\"\",\"d\":\"\",\"pl\":\"United States\",\"desc\":\"\"},{\"t\":\"OTHER_EVENT\",\"ti\":\"Arrival\",\"d\":\"\",\"pl\":\"United States\",\"desc\":\"\"},{\"t\":\"OTHER_FACT\",\"ti\":\"Barford Plantation \",\"d\":\"\",\"pl\":\"\",\"desc\":\"\"}],\"sketch\":\"\",\"mem\":30,\"src\":23},{\"pos\":5,\"gen\":12,\"id\":\"LZ6B-6XC\",\"name\":\"Katherine Dale\",\"life\":\"1652–1703\",\"bp\":\"St. Mary's Parish, Caroline, Virginia, British Colonial America\",\"dp\":\"White Chapel Magisterial District, Lancaster, Virginia, British Colonial America\",\"states\":[\"Virginia\"],\"primary\":\"Virginia\",\"score\":2,\"interesting\":false,\"ev\":[{\"t\":\"OTHER_EVENT\",\"ti\":\"Will\",\"d\":\"4 August 1674\",\"pl\":\"Lancaster, Virginia, British Colonial America\",\"desc\":\"\"}],\"sketch\":\"\",\"mem\":9,\"src\":14},{\"pos\":10,\"gen\":13,\